Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.05,OP5,,0,0,0,,OP Start
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.65,0:00:20.09,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I put together dried up words...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.92,0:00:28.83,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}but all I want to do is convey\N my simple feelings to you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.83,0:00:34.27,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}The faint wind that blew from that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.27,0:00:38.40,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}I threw it away in yesterday's ruins
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.42,0:00:44.55,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}So I can live today with you with a smile
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.09,0:00:52.19,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}But still, this incident will\N continue to trouble you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:57.08,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}That's why it must be a goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.08,0:01:04.12,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Now we just try to understand\N each other until nothing remains
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.12,0:01:11.27,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}And eventually, we will realize\N that it was everything to us
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.27,0:01:18.01,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Sadness will run down our cheeks,\N creating a river of tears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.42,0:01:28.97,OP5,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(0,1700)}Trembling thoughts will become a strong\N whirl and melt together into one
Comment: 0,0:01:29.97,0:01:30.04,OP5,,0,0,0,,OP End
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the other one?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.27,0:01:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.27,0:01:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.30,0:01:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of the rest.\NGo wash your eyes in that river.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.57,0:02:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my ability...\Nspecializing in assassination, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't beat me by just having\Na good nose and nails...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.25,0:02:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't beat my ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.34,0:02:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Akamaru... I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.94,0:02:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Akamaru...\NWe've always done things together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.78,0:02:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We were together\Nwhenever and wherever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.73,0:02:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,However this one time, I'm sunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.07,0:02:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,My cells can swim inside\Nyour body as I wish,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.86,0:02:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and I can even create parts\Nthat are only you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.70,0:02:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words,\Na little bit of a fusion condition...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.54,0:02:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,a sharing of the flesh is what it'll be.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.25,0:02:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A sharing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.63,0:02:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.14,0:02:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And a cruel way of killing\Nthat only I can accomplish...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:03:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the gradual scraping off\Nof just your cells!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.64,0:03:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.48,0:03:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.20,0:03:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If I do this...\Nwhat's gonna happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.91,0:03:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Suicide?! That's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.50,0:03:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Die with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.44,0:03:39.44,Sign_1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(456,467)}To Each His Own Battle
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.30,0:03:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,To Each His Own Battle
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.70,0:04:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.04,0:04:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just as I thought...\NWe are sharing one body, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.26,0:04:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.26,0:04:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Entering my opponent's body\Nto avoid any attacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.84,0:04:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that is my Jutsu's greatest advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.44,0:04:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There hasn't been\Na single one before now
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.27,0:04:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,who's done this sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.27,0:04:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you in pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.23,0:04:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,All right then, let's get comfortable now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.24,0:04:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, you idiot!\NStop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.91,0:04:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.64,0:05:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There's not enough blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.91,0:05:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.71,0:05:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.89,0:05:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So he left his little dog behind\Nand fled.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.18,0:05:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the right decision,\Nbut he's more cold-hearted than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.55,0:06:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.75,0:06:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It couldn't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.72,0:06:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What a relief...\NHe's still breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.56,0:06:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:07:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Akamaru... You really gave it your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.09,0:07:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of you, I was able to hold up\Nthe enemy for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.84,0:07:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We've caused injuries\Nupon the enemy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.22,0:07:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's enough... You've done enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.53,0:07:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,His name is Akamaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.54,0:07:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom... Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.75,0:07:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,F rom today, you'll take care of him...\NOkay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.09,0:07:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I will?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.02,0:08:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Kiba. Nice to meet you, Akamaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.07,0:08:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.13,0:08:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been together forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.97,0:08:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice catch, Akamaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.18,0:08:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, you did well!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.06,0:08:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.90,0:08:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Be more serious about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.91,0:09:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop being such a baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.37,0:09:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.59,0:09:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Kiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.35,0:09:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.99,0:09:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Akamaru and you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.38,0:09:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,the two of you need\Nto become strong together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.68,0:09:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,With Akamaru... Together?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.19,0:09:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Akamaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.70,0:09:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to go Akamaru! You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.24,0:09:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mid-air Dynamic Marking!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Next is mid-air triple somersault!\NTake your aim!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.68,0:09:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.56,0:10:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.28,0:10:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be together forever\Nfrom now on too...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.66,0:10:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll protect you from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.42,0:10:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.59,0:10:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Setting up a trap on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.48,0:10:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.65,0:11:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Sakon! Where are you?! Sakon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.46,0:11:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.50,0:11:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.26,0:11:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Blah blah blah.\NYou're such a nuisance, Big Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.12,0:11:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Your yelling stings my eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.56,0:11:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.93,0:11:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill him... is what I'd like to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.10,0:11:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's almost time for my sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.56,0:11:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Capture those bastards alive in my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.73,0:11:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,When I wake up,\NI'll kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.24,0:11:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Sakon?\NCapture them alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.74,0:11:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I got it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.12,0:11:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.87,0:11:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The killing part,\Nwe'll do it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.53,0:12:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If I carelessly attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,he dodges\Nand I end up attacking myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.73,0:12:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.77,0:12:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Willow Dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.13,0:13:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.32,0:13:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Bones?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.41,0:13:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my... Kekkei Genkai.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.07,0:14:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this guy...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.99,0:14:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he attacking with bones sticking out\Nfrom all over his body?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.53,0:15:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He's grabbed his own bone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.29,0:15:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.54,0:15:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He's turning the bone...\Ninto a sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.60,0:15:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's futile. It's not just ordinary bone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.40,0:15:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The highest density bone is hard as steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.97,0:15:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?! I 'll break that bone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.83,0:15:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I possess Five Dances.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.33,0:16:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better not think\Nyou know my strength after just this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.99,0:16:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.46,0:16:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll specially show you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.59,0:16:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the Camellia Dance next.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.14,0:16:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll crush you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.45,0:16:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.78,0:16:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Substitution?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.87,0:16:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.87,0:16:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.05,0:16:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They're getting closer and closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.72,0:17:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.57,0:17:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't good, traces of blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.27,0:17:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, I did save Akamaru\Nfor the time being,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.91,0:17:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,but maybe I went too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.60,0:17:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This smell...\NWhat does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.40,0:17:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why... Why is it that even those guys\Nare headed to a place like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.77,0:17:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.24,0:17:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case,\Nwe need to leave this place quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.28,0:18:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.24,0:18:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starting to feel light-headed\Nfrom the pain and loss of blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.58,0:18:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,My body won't move at all either...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.96,0:18:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Akamaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.37,0:18:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He left just his coat...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.50,0:18:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.93,0:19:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So he fled by floating down the river...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.97,0:19:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.02,0:19:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.15,0:19:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.28,0:19:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.45,0:19:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I've cornered you, you stinking rat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.75,0:19:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty impressive...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.88,0:19:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You timed it well to scatter\Nthe three to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.96,0:19:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have practiced quite a bit, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.05,0:19:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Since it's a pretty complicated song...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.60,0:19:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.89,0:19:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only did you\Nimmediately understand
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.43,0:19:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,that I'm manipulating these guys\Nwith my flute,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.39,0:19:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,you understood how difficult this song is.\NYou're a pretty impressive punk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.90,0:19:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can't completely\Nunderstand this song.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.28,0:20:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so right...\Nsince art is so foreign to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.74,0:20:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But since she uses that flute\Nto manipulate,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.21,0:20:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,it means that song must contain\Nindividually specific sound patterns
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.54,0:20:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to control each and every movement\Nof those guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.01,0:20:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty confident\Nwhen it comes to just analyzing,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.70,0:20:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,but this time it's not looking good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.39,0:20:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason is that
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.02,0:20:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand\Nmusical notes whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.98,0:20:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no one that's heard\Nthis song and lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Finale, Ninth Passage,\NDemon Revolution!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.62,0:20:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The melody's changed!
