Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.77,0:21:17.86,ED8,,0,0,0,,And you smiled
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.11,0:21:20.40,ED8,,0,0,0,,For the first time, I was able to speak
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.40,0:21:23.20,ED8,,0,0,0,,In my own words
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.20,0:21:28.84,ED8,,0,0,0,,Would you think it was\Na bother if I approached you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.84,0:21:34.25,ED8,,0,0,0,,Despite my doubts,\NI worked up my courage
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.66,0:21:40.18,ED8,,0,0,0,,My clumsy attempts with words
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.18,0:21:45.85,ED8,,0,0,0,,You listened without turning away
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.60,0:21:51.97,ED8,,0,0,0,,No wonder I get carried away by you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.37,0:21:59.04,ED8,,0,0,0,,But you don't feel anything for me, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.42,0:22:02.24,ED8,,0,0,0,,I feel so sad
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.24,0:22:03.21,ED8,,0,0,0,,But...
